About Us
Welcome!
Are you looking for a special place to enjoy beautiful scenery and the finest fishing that Lake Okeechobee has to offer? Well then, look no further! We've recently remodeled our Lodge & RV community making this park a great place to call home during your visit to the area. We are a quiet & older community with family friendly services for our residents and vacationers.
"Come fish in our backyard!"
Our Park Offers:
- Waterfront with direct access to Lake Okeechobee, and only two miles to Henry Creek Lock.
- Concrete boat ramp, updated boat docks, and fish cleaning station.
- 30-50 Amp full hook up sites, paved roads, shaded sites, and pull-thru availability.
- Dining pavilion area overlooking the water with a porch swing to enjoy sunrises and sunsets. The inside is furnished with tables, a flat screen TV, coffee/tea station, and game boards. - High speed wifi, showers, coin laundromat, and dumpster.
- Remodeled furnished studios and lodges.
- Open all year with daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly rental options.
